Industries

Fire protection

With built in support for the fire protection industry (AS1851-2005 and AS1851-2012), as well as other Australian Standards relevant to building maintenance, Uptick helps you manage your programme maintenance / planned prevantative maintenance schedules easily while collecting the data you need to stay compliant, easily generate quotes, and run your business efficiently.

Auditing and essential safety measures

Uptick allows you to easily generate your annual compliance certificate (AESMR, ASMR, AFSS, Form 6 and Form 56), audit the attendance of companies, and provide your customers deep insight into their portfolios.
